w.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/south-france-wedding-planner-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4509 alignleft\" title=\"Alan Roberts lead singer with The Blah Blahs\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/wedding-entertainment-south-france.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"639\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/wedding-entertainment-south-france.jpg 750w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/wedding-entertainment-south-france-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/03\/wedding-entertainment-south-france-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 639px) 100vw, 639px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>Photographers<\/strong>, our friend Peter the vicar, <strong>vintage wedding cars<\/strong>, hair and make-up, <strong>a DJ<\/strong>, Fireworks and of course the legendary Alan Roberts and the Blah Blahs were soon organised and booked as no <strong>Cote d\u2019Azur<\/strong> stone was left unturned in this particular bride\u2019s pursuit of perfection. It was a perfect wedding and even though the Provencal sunshine stayed away it still turned out to be a beautiful day and a great party that <strong>Red Radish<\/strong> was particularly proud to be part of. The bride and groom were the loveliest couple and we hope that they will are pretty sure that they will go on to become great friends, just like Claire and Paul.<strong><br \/>\n<\/strong><a title=\"Customer Reference\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2013\/03\/people-still-talk-about-the-cheeseboard-now\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><br \/>\nWhy not see some more photographs and what the bride and Groom thought about Red Radish here<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p>For for a free and competitive quotation call or <a href=\"mailto:wayne@red-radish.com\"><strong>email Red 